version_description:
- Fix for not being able to establish a VPN connection on iOS6.
- Fix for not being able to start a VPN connection on iOS8 when initiated via URL scheme if there are no existing configurations already in Edge Client.

- An optimized UI for iPhone 6 and iPhone 6 Plus devices
- Support for Apple iOS 8 widgets, making it faster for users to initiate VPN connections
- A diagnostics section that provides details on system and network information

- Improvements to web logon authentication
- bug fixes
Fixed issue with rendering of external authentication pages in weblogon.

Edge Client support for iPad Pro
Support for Server Name Indication (SNI)
Bugs fixes and security updates

iOS 10 Support
Fixed Edge Client application freeze during certain MDM configuration conditions.

• User Interface and Branding Changes: F5 will be changing the name of F5 BIG-IP Edge Client for iOS to F5 Access for iOS. With the new name change, there will be branding, icon, and user-interface changes.
• TouchID Support & Device Authentication
- Renamed the application from F5 Access to F5 Access Legacy, updated icon
